snippet.title: The Starbites - Trailer | TGS 2024
snippet.description:
This brand new action RPG takes you to the planet Bitter and lets you take control of a topsy-turvy crew of mech pilots. Explore the world, engage in turn-based battles, and chase your destiny in The Starbites.

#TheStarbites #Gaming #Games
